main event: A sighting of a large silver object along with two smaller blinking objects moving in a circular path on July 22, 1955.
interesting points: The observation lasted for 15 minutes,Three objects were observed - one large and two small,Observation was documented with photographs,Photographs are to be analyzed by ATIC,The report is part of Project Blue Book investigations.
sighted object: one large silver object and two smaller blinking objects
witness description: Observer who reported the sighting and took photographs
